txt.en: From within Kêr Bréin, a powerful hobgoblin leads the raids on Skarháld and keeps watch on the newly-laid eggs of the Frost-horde.
Mission: The Snows of Kêr Bréin
'You've done well, [placeholder]! Let us report your success to Hórin!'
Your mission is to defeat the powerful hobgoblin, Rukhnúl, at Kêr Bréin.
